@notice Clears the blacklist for a given token by incrementing its version.
 @dev This effectively resets the transfer history for that token.
 @param token The address of the token whose blacklist should be cleared.

@title Token Repository
 @notice A contract that allows owners to transfer BEP20 tokens from the repository.
 @dev Only owners are allowed to initiate transfers. For each token, a transfer to a specific address
      can only occur once per version. Clearing the blacklist for a token is achieved by incrementing its version.
